*Separator Parameters* allows to configure separation constructions, that will be used to separate the element instances on rendering.

![Separator parameters](http://joolanders.github.io/Docs/docs/DownloadPro/images/element_position_separator.png)

- **By** - Allows to separate downloadable items by chosen separator *(Chose from the list)*.
- **Custom By** - Allows to specify custom separator for download links.
- **Class** - Allows to add custom class to download link.
- **Fix HTML** - After the separator was applied, this feature will try to fix erroneous HTML code of the element output. Use carefully and disable if any issue shows up with the rendered result.